projects.name: Online Voting System Using Java
projects.description: Developed an Online Voting System using Java Swing. The application provides a user-friendly interface for voters to cast their votes for one of three parties. It includes features such as data entry fields for voters name and phone number, radio buttons for party selection, and buttons for submitting votes and resending the form. The system maintains a count of votes for each party, demonstrating proficiency in GUI development and event handling in Java.
